                      style="font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;font-size: 22px;line-height: 32px;text-align: center;color: #7E7E7E;margin-bottom: 80px;">
                      Link is valid till only 1 hour</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" border="0">
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td align="left">
                    <div class="p-20" style="padding: 55px 0;background: #DFF9FF;">
                      <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                        <img src="https://cascade-content.s3.amazonaws.com/resumes/paddleboatLogo.png" alt="paddleboat"
                          style="display:block; margin:0 auto;">
                      </div>
